General Notes

Title Summary
Beam Labels By giving the tags a more efficient label this will help identifying issues, find their install location without the use of marking plans, understanding schedulers intensions and greatly increase faster productivity. 
Confirmations Tracking By using this sheet to track when control codes are confirmed will help with identifying when mistakes happen in one location instead of searching through all the emails trying to find when something was confirmed.
Delivery Projections By using this emaple sheets to create a projected delivery date for items can better prepare the supply to have a window to fabricate. This is not a confirmation bible but a good way to stay ahead of the program. This also will help identify any missed items early by all parties involved.
